Delete the Object Store file of a specific organization and key. The /object/delete API accepts requests in the following format:

DeleteObjectStoreRequest Model - Request to delete Object Store metadata of a specific organization and key.
organizationId string
required
example: 5cad178b20a1d52567b534553413b691
Organization ID we'd like to delete the Object Store file from.
key string
required
example: key1
Key to the Object Store file.
Example 
{
  "organizationId": "5cad178b20a1d52567b534553413b691",
  "key": "key1"
}
